commit.title: [print] Restrict use of "debug" Termops printer.
commit.message:
[print] Restrict use of "debug" Termops printer.

The `Termops.print_*` functions are declared as a debug printers, but
they are pervasively used in non-debug code, and in fact, replaced by
the real printers defined in `printing`.

This seems to point to a design problem in the printing system and in
particular in its location.

We mark the users, and switch some from `Termops` to `Printer`.
